description: Need a neat treat to beat the Alabama heat? Well, it sure is nice that that this Magic City cart is pushing the “brrrrrr” through Birmingham, along with their delicious, authentic Italian Ice. Magic City Sweet Ice mixes only the highest-quality ingredients, like fresh fruits and juices into their ice (as opposed to squirting them on top) for a fat-free, dairy-free, cholesterol-free, gluten-free, high fructose corn syrup-free, yet tasty and flavorFUL frozen confection of absolute perfection.
name: Magic City Sweet Ice
